name: Saint 01 - Snakes around Us / Santo 01 - Serpentes entre Nós
description: Being a Latin American person means that you live in a world that is constantly subjulgated and discriminated. So we have to create our own Saints and symbologies based on what we live and see around here. Its a mechanism of selfcare and a way to glorify the good things that we (and only we) have here. Our culture, our nature, our colours
